sawfowl.commandpack.api.commands.raw

Interface RawPlayerCommand

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.spongepowered.api.command.Command, org.spongepowered.api.command.Command.Raw, PluginCommand, RawCommand

    public interface RawPlayerCommand
extends RawCommand
    This interface is designed to simplify the creation of Raw commands.
    Commands created using this interface can only be used by players.
